title: Energy (Music Video) - Drake [7.10.15] *NEW*
description:
But the biggest news of all was the release of his video for "Energy," the first video cut from his February album / mixtape If You're Reading This It's Too Late.

This thing's a doozy: it features Drake playing a bunch of other celebrities and public figures, including Oprah, Justin Bieber (in his underwear ad getup), Miley Cyrus (in the "Wrecking Ball" video), Kanye West (in the "Bound 2" video), Rob Ford, LeBron James, and President Obama. You'll have to head to Drake's Connect page within Apple Music if you want to see the whole thing for yourself, but we've captured GIFs of the funniest moments for your viewing pleasure
